  <releases>
    <release version="1.6.4" date="2025-12-15">
      <url type="details">https://github.com/benjamimgois/goverlay/releases/tag/1.6.4</url>
      <description>
        <ul>
          <li>Another day, another release...</li>
          <li>This small release brings a FSR version management system, now you can choose betwen the latest FSR DLL (with ML features for RDNA4) or stick to the INT8 version that keeps RDNA2 and 3 compatibility.</li>
          <li>Also there's another regression fix catched by @LuanVSO. Thanks dude !</li>
          <li>Major Features:</li>
          <li>FSR4 Variant Management System: Switch between FP8 (latest) and INT8 (4.0.2) variants</li>
          <li>Automatic folder creation and setup during OptiScaler update</li>
          <li>User-selectable via dropdown menu</li>
          <li>Persistent configuration with automatic restoration</li>
          <li>Bug Fixes:</li>
          <li>FPS limit offset now correctly handles zero (unlimited) values (PR #222 by @LuanVSO)</li>
          <li>OBS: Delete your old FGMOD folder and install it again so everything works smoothly</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
  </releases>

